cu.explanation_en: Setting the AMF IP address to an invalid value will cause network connectivity issues and prevent proper AMF communication.

du.explanation_en: Setting the minimum RX/TX time to zero will invalidate timing configurations and prevent proper signal processing.
du.explanation_zh: 將最小 RX/TX 時間設定為零會使時序配置無效，並阻止正確的信號處理。
